{{Quote|The Rest and Sleep 寝る is designed for relaxation and restful sleep. Each room offers a serene, mesmerizing atmosphere crafted to help you unwind. Soft lighting and calming ambient music create a peaceful escape from daily stress, letting you fully immerse in tranquility. This world is your sanctuary to relax and enjoy the moment. Time to sleep! VRC Group: https://vrc.group/SLEEP.7324}}

'''Rest and Sleep 寝る''' is a sleep world. Published in February 2021, it consists of multiple locations, focusing on "coziness" and relaxation to help users sleep. The world is available on PC or both PC and Android through different world ids. 

==Locations==
The world is separated into 4 different locations, noted by the name over doors.
===Sleep===
===Rest===
===Chill===
===Roof===

==World variants==
Rest and Sleep has 2 world variants, the main version is PC only, while the [https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_e2df1e94-75c6-439c-ac80-eaf0eda3d501 other version] supports PC and Android. There are no differences between the 2 variants besides the [[Platforms|platform]] requirement.

